{"tid":1905594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】美國華盛頓州一護理中心52人現病徵","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T12:25:56.000Z","uid":13468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8a0c85f00193f0dfc2ed2070f54b733bb9c9ad","tid":1905594,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】美國華盛頓州一護理中心52人現病徵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國上周六（2月29日）出現首宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎死亡個案，患者居住的華盛頓州宣布進入緊急狀態。華盛頓州西雅圖及金縣衛生部官員Jeff Duchin稱，該州3宗確診病例有兩宗均與柯克蘭護理中心Life Care Center有關，中心還有52人出現呼吸道感染徵狀，已被安排進行病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，上述兩宗確診個案的患者，分別是該中心一名女職員及一名院友。出現病徵者則包括27名居民及25名職員。暫未知首宗死亡個案是否亦與該中心有關。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/KIRO7/USA Today）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200301/s00005/1583047640186/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%8F%AF%E7%9B%9B%E9%A0%93%E5%B7%9E%E4%B8%80%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%8352%E4%BA%BA%E7%8F%BE%E7%97%85%E5%BE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200301%2Fs00005%2F1583047640186%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%259B%259B%25E9%25A0%2593%25E5%25B7%259E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%258352%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BE%25B5&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGopNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=53725268\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200301%2Fs00005%2F1583047640186%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%259B%259B%25E9%25A0%2593%25E5%25B7%259E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%258352%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2597%2585%2